Fayrasku wuxuu isticmaalaa habab kala duwan si uu u kiciyo caabuq, unugyada qaadashada antigen, isku-darka nooca I ee interferons (IFNs) si loo xakameeyo faafitaanka fayraska, taas oo dardar gelineysa fayraska antigen macrophage phagocytosis.
