Si kastaba ha noqotee, wararka sheegaya in dadka ay ku qaadi karaan fayraska in ka badan laba toddobaad iyagoo aan muujin calaamadaha iyo in bukaannada ka soo kabsaday isbitaalka ay mar kale ku qaadi karaan fayraska ayaa noqon kara digniin lagu kordhinayo xilliga karantiilinta.
