Si loola dagaallamo cudurka SARS-CoV-2, kooxdeena waxay soo saartay tilmaamo talooyin deg deg ah oo lagu daabacay khadka tooska ah ee Military Medical Research on Febraayo 06,2020.
Tan iyo markii la daabacay, waxaa soo jiitay dareen aad u weyn.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, ogow in COVID-19 ay tahay cudur cusub, fahamkeena iyo aqoonteena ayaa si tartiib tartiib ah u sii kordheysa iyadoo lagu saleynayo natiijooyinka cilmi baarista ee hadda jira iyo dhaqanka tijaabada bukaanka, sidaa darteed, hababka baaritaanka iyo daaweynta ayaa sidoo kale si joogto ah loo hagaajiyaa.
Tusaale ahaan, Tilmaamaha Baaritaanka iyo Daaweynta COVID-19 ee ay soo saartay Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Jamhuuriyadda Dadka Shiinaha (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), oo soo saaray toddobo daabacaad oo guud ah intii u dhaxaysay Janaayo 16, 2020 ilaa Maarso 3, 2020, ayaa la beddelay qaar ka mid ah macnaha guud.
Hadda tilmaamaheena ayaa helay jawaab celin ka timid iyaga, kuwaas oo soo jeediyay qiimeyn sahlan oo ku saleysan khibradooda bukaan socodka.
