b'Angiotensin -converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku jira dusha sare ee unugyada sanbabada, xididdada dhiigga, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay ka dhigeysaa bartilmaameed daawo rajo leh oo lagu daaweynayo cudurrada xididdada dhiigga iyadoo yareynaysa heerarka angostatin-II iyo kordhinta Ang (1-7) oo ka hortagta waxqabadka enzyme-ka isbeddelka angotensin (ACE). ACE2 waxay u adeegtaa sida bartilmaameedka gelitaanka unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus.
Enzyme-ka aadanaha waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angostatin-enzyme 2 waa zinc-ka birta ku jira ee ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada iyo unugyada kale.
Boreyinka ACE2 waxaa loo qoondeeyay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waa nooc ka mid ah daaha I ee mararka qaarkood faafa, taas oo ah sababta oo ah enzyme-ka wuxuu leeyahay domain firfircoon oo ku yaal dusha sanbabada iyo qaybaha kale ee jirka.
Qaybta dibadda ee ACE2 waxaa ka gooyay qaybta gudaha ee unugyada enzyme kale oo la yiraahdo Shadas, taas oo keentay in loo sii daayo wareegga dhiigga sida borotiinka lagu milmi karo, ugu dambeynna loo sii daayo sidii kaabsoor.
ACE2 waxaa laga helaa inta badan xubnaha jirka: ACE2 waxay ku xidhan tahay inta badan unugyada alveolar ee sanbabada nooca II, unugyada mindhicirka yar, unugyada xididdada dhiigga iyo xididdada dhiigga iyo unugyada muruqyada jilicsan ee xididdada dhiigga ee inta badan xubnaha jirka.
ACE2 mRNA waxaa lagu qeexaa maskaxda, garabka, hypothalamus iyo unugyada maskaxda.
Shaqada ugu weyn ee ACE2 waa inay noqoto dheelitirka ACE.
ACE waxay u wareejisaa hormoonka angiotensin I ee loo yaqaan 'angiotensin II' ee xannibaadda xididdada.
ACE2 waxay gooysaa phenylalanine, oo ah amino acid-ka karboksiil-ka ah ee ka soo baxa angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) oo ku jira xayawaanka, waxayna u beddeleysaa biyo-qaadista angiotestin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay baabi'in kartaa [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A iyo ghrelin oo ay ku jiraan dhowr peptides oo kale.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa xuubka SLC6A19, oo ah gaadiidka amino acid ee dhexdhexaadka ah, waxaana la ogyahay inay ku lug leedahay cudurka 'Hartnap'.
Sida borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 wuxuu u adeegaa sida barta ugu weyn ee unugyada loogu galo qaar ka mid ah fayrasyada coronavirus, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (viruska keena SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (viruska keena COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, borotiinnada S1 ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 waxay ku xidhan yihiin unugyada ACE2 ee unugyada enzyme-ka, taas oo u oggolaanaysa fayraska iyo enzymes-ka inay galaan unugyada gudaha iyo wareegga.
Nidaamkan gelitaanka wuxuu sidoo kale u baahan yahay in horudhac loo sameeyo borotiinka S ee TMPRSS2, oo ah habka ugu wanaagsan ee loo helo daaweynta baaritaanka. Tani waxay keentay in qaar ka mid ah ay u maleynayaan in ay ka caawin karto la dagaalanka infekshanka iyadoo hoos loo dhigayo heerarka ACE2 ee unugyada.
