Sababta saxda ah ee kala duwanaanta jinsiga lama yaqaan, laakiin hiddo-wadaha iyo astaamaha ayaa laga yaabaa inay sabab u yihiin.
Kala duwanaanshaha cudurada galmada, sigaarka sigaar cabista, sida cadaadiska dhiigga oo hooseeya, ayaa sababi kara in heerka dhimashada ragga uu ka sarreeyo heerka dumarka.
