Ilaa Abriil 2020, dowladda Mareykanka ma la socotay xogta galmada ee la xiriirta cudurrada COVID-19.
Cilmi baaristu waxay muujineysaa in cudurrada sida Ebola, HIV, hargabka iyo SARS ay si ka duwan u dhacaan ragga iyo dumarka.
Tiro badan oo ka mid ah shaqaalaha caafimaadka, gaar ahaan kalkaalisada caafimaadka, waa haween, waxayna u badan tahay inay ku dhacaan fayraska.
Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa 11 Febraayo 2020 magaca rasmiga ah ee cudurka loo yaqaan COVID-19.
Sida uu sheegay Agaasimaha Guud ee Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka Theodros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Carbon Corona, waa fayraska ugu horreeya ee la aqoonsaday markii uu cudurka, cudurka iyo cudurka ku dhacay 19 qof: 31 Diseembar 2019.
Si looga fogaado takoorka, iyadoo la raacayo talooyinka caalamiga ah, magaca waxaa loo doortay in laga fogaado in lagu wareejiyo meel juqraafi ah (tusaale ahaan Shiinaha), noocyo xayawaan ama koox dad ah. Fayraska keena COVID-19 waxaa loo yaqaan 'Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome 2' (SARS-CoV-2).
Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa sidoo kale isticmaala ereyada "virus COVID-19" iyo "virus-ka keena COVID-19" ee warbaahinta rasmiga ah.
"Cudurkan iyo fayraska waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan ""Coronavirus""".
Fayraska iyo cudurka waxaa loo yaqaan 'coronavirus' iyo 'Wuhan coronavirus' markii ugu horreysay ee laga helay Wuhan, Shiinaha.
Bishii Janaayo 2020, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa soo jeediyay in 2020-nCov iyo 2019-nCoV ee cudurka neefsashada degdegga ah loo isticmaalo magacyo ku meelgaar ah ee fayraska iyo cudurka iyadoo la raacayo tilmaamaha 2015 ee ku saabsan isticmaalka meelaha ka baxsan magacyada fayraska.
Magacyada COVID-19 iyo SARS-CoV-2 waxaa la magacaabay 11 Febraayo, 2020.
Sababtoo ah xaddidaadaha awoodda ee silsiladaha sahayda caadiga ah, qaar ka mid ah soo saarayaasha dhijitaalka ah ayaa daabacaya qalabka daryeelka caafimaadka sida sanka iyo qaybaha hawo-qaadista.
Tusaale ahaan, isbitaal Talyaani ah ayaa u baahan waalka hawo-qaboojinta si degdeg ah, marka alaab-qeybiyaha uu bixin karo waqtiga loo baahan yahay, marka bilowga maxalliga ah ee Blast-Nurse uu daabacay 100 waalka maalin kasta oo loo baahan yahay habeenkii.
Tan iyo markii uu dillaacay COVID-19, macluumaadka ku saabsan asalka, qiyaasta, ka hortagga, daaweynta iyo dhinacyada kale ee cudurka iyo macluumaadka ayaa si dhakhso leh ugu faafa internetka.
Dadka ayaa u muuqda inay awood u leeyihiin inay fayraska u faafiyaan xayawaanka kale.
Daraasaddu ma helin wax caddayn ah oo ah faafitaanka fayraska ee doofaarka, dabacasaha iyo digaagga.
Ma jiro daawo ama tallaal lagu daaweeyo cudurka.
Cilmi baaris caalami ah oo ku saabsan tallaalada iyo daawooyinka COVID-19 ayaa waxaa sameynaya hay'adaha dowladda, kooxaha tacliinta iyo cilmi baarayaasha warshadaha.
Bishii Maarso, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa aasaasay tijaabooyin 'Solidarity Experiment' si loo qiimeeyo saameynta daaweynta ee afar kiimiko oo ka hortag ah fayraska oo la sheegay inay waxtar badan leeyihiin.
Ma jiro tallaal, laakiin hay'ado kala duwan ayaa si firfircoon u horumarinaya murashaxiinta tallaalka.
SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV-2 ayaa horey loogu isticmaalay SARS-CoV, sababtoo ah labaduba waxay isticmaalaan ACE2 receptor receptor si ay u galaan unugyada.
Waxaa jira saddex nooc oo tallaal ah oo la baaray.
Marka hore, cilmi baarayaashu waxay higsanayaan inay abuuraan tallaal guud oo ka hortag ah fayraska.
Isticmaalka fayraska noocan ah, ha ahaado mid firfircoon ama mid dhintay, ayaa ah in la yareeyo awoodda difaaca jirka ee jirka ee cudurrada daran si looga jawaabo nuglaanshaha cusub ee COVID-19.
Istaraatijiyad labaad waa tallaalka yar, kaas oo loogu talagalay in la abuuro tallaal la xakameyn karo qaybaha qaarkood ee fayraska.
Xaaladda SARS-CoV-2, cilmi baarista noocan oo kale ah waxay diiradda saareysaa borotiinka S-spike, oo ka caawiya fayraska inuu xakameeyo soo-dhoweeyaha ACE2 enzyme.
Habka saddexaad waa tallaalka nucleic acid (DNA ama RNA tallaal waa hab cusub oo lagu abuuro tallaal).
Mid ka mid ah hababkan waa in la tijaabiyaa tallaalada tijaabada ah ee badbaadada iyo waxtarka. Tijaabada ugu horreysa ee bukaan-socodka ee tallaalka ayaa ka bilaabatay Seattle 16 Maarso 2020 iyadoo lagu daray afar mutadawiciin.
Tallaalku wuxuu ka kooban yahay koodhka hidde-wadaha ee aan waxyeello lahayn oo laga soo qaatay fayraska cudurka u keena. In kasta oo la soo jeediyay horumar ku saleysan unugyada difaaca ee nugul ee loogu talagalay diyaarinta tallaalka SARS-COV-2, tani waa muran.
In ka badan 300 tijaabooyin caafimaad oo socda ayaa socda ilaa Abriil 2020.
Waxaa dib loo eegay daaweyntii hore loo oggolaaday ee duumada, oo ay ku jiraan toddoba daraasadood oo la oggolaaday oo ay ku jiraan afar hydrochloroquine ama chloroquine.
Inta badan daawooyinka loo isticmaalo ee loo yaqaan 'anti-viral drugs' ayaa lagu sameeyay cilmi baarista Shiinaha, oo lagu soo warramey dhamaadka Abriil sagaal tijaabo oo cutubka III ah oo lagu sameeyay dalal badan.
Ilaa Abriil 2020, waxaa la sameeyay qiimeyn isbeddel ah oo ku saabsan horumarka bukaan socodka ee tallaalka COVID-19 iyo murashaxiinta dawooyinka. Daawooyinka badan ee jira ee fayraska ka hortaga ee loo yaqaan 'reflovir, chloroquine iyo hydrochlorothiacin, lopeavia / rutanvir iyo lopenavir / rudonavir oo ay weheliso interferon beta ayaa lagu qiimeynayaa daaweynta COVID-19.
Waxaa jira caddayn macquul ah oo ku saabsan waxtarka sicir-dhimista illaa Maarso 2020.
Bukaannada lagu daaweeyey daaweynta naxariista-isticmaalka ayaa muujiyay horumar caafimaad.
Tijaabooyinka caafimaad ee wajiga III ayaa ka socda Mareykanka, Shiinaha iyo Talyaaniga. Chloroquine, oo horey loogu isticmaali jiray daaweynta duumada, waxaa markii ugu horreysay lagu bartay Shiinaha bishii Febraayo 2020.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, waxaa jira baaqyo dib u eegis ah oo loogu talagalay dib u eegista asxaabta cilmi baarista.
Saraakiisha caafimaadka ee Kuuriya iyo Shiinaha ayaa kugula talinaya isticmaalka chloroquine.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, Machadka Wuhan ee Fayraska ayaa tilmaamay in hal garaam oo maalinle ah la talinayo, laakiin laba jeer qiyaastaas ay khatar badan tahay oo ay u badan tahay inay dhimasho.
28/2020, Xulashada Dhakhaatiirta Daaweynta Dadka qaba COVID-19 waxay ogolaatay isticmaalka degdegga ah ee hydroxychloroquine iyo chloroquine. Tilmaamaha Shiinaha ee daabacaadda 7-aad ayaa sidoo kale ku jira isticmaalka Intervirone, Ribavirin ama Umfenovirone ee COVID-19.
Xogta hore waxay soo jeedineysaa in heerarka sare ee ribavirin ay lagama maarmaan u yihiin tallaalka SARS-CoV-2 ee vitro.
Ka dib markii ay muujisay xoojinta cadaadiska hoose ee SARS-CoV-2, waxaa lagu taliyey in Nitazoxanide loo isticmaalo in lagu daro daraasadaha vivo. Daraasadaha ayaa muujiyay in isticmaalka borotiinka sare ee 'trans-tissue protease serine 2' (TMPRSS2) uu muhiim u yahay SARS-CoV-2 iyada oo loo marayo isdhexgalka qaataha ACE2.
Cilmi-baarista loo sameeyay chloroquine iyo hydrochlorocurine oo ay weheliso ama aan lahayn arthromycin waxay leeyihiin xaddidaadyo waaweyn oo bulshada caafimaadka ay ka hortageyso inay daaweyntaan daaweyntaas iyada oo aan la helin daraasad dheeri ah. Oseltamivir ma dhaxlo SARS-CoV-2 vitro mana laha door la yaqaan daaweynta COVID-19.
Duufaanta cytokine waxay noqon kartaa mid adag marxaladaha dambe ee COVID-19 ee daran.
Waxaa jira caddayn muujinaysa in hydroxychloroquine ay yeelan karto astaamaha anti-cytokine wave. Tocilizumab waxaa lagu daray tilmaamaha daaweynta Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha ka dib markii la dhammeystiray daraasad yar.
Tijaabooyinka heer qaran oo aan la qorsheyn ee wajiga 2 ayaa ka socda Talyaaniga ka dib markii ay ku guuleysteen dadka qaba cudurrada daran.
Marka lagu daro baaritaanka dhiigga ee Sam Fritzstein si loo ogaado hirarka isotonin, waxaa loogu talagalay in lagu hortago horumarka noocan oo kale ah ee loo maleynayo inay sabab u yihiin dhimashada dadka la dhaawacay.
Interleukin-6 receptor antagonist ayaa si gaar ah loogu oggolaaday FDA iyadoo lagu saleynayo daraasadaha ku saleysan daaweynta CAR T cell therapy, daaweynta steroidal reversible ethoxine-ka sii deynta cudurka, oo la daabacay 2017.
Ilaa hadda ma jiraan wax xog ah oo la xakameyn karo oo muujinaya in tokylaseem uu yahay daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo loogu talagalay CRS.
Unugyada difaaca ee ay sameeyeen dadka ka soo kabsaday COVID-19 ayaa la baaray in loo soo jeediyo habka tallaalka ee loogu talagalay dadka u baahan unugyada difaaca ee la nadiifiyey oo la kaydiyay.
Istaraatijiyadani waxay keentay natiijooyin aan ku kalsoonaan karin waayo-aragnimada SARS.
Xaddidida fayraska / xakamaynta waa tallaabo la qorsheeyay oo ka dhigi karta daawada ka hortagga ee SARS-CoV-2 inay noqoto dhexdhexaad difaaca.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, istaraatiijiyad kale oo ay ka mid yihiin anti-cellular cytotoxic iyo / ama fungicotosis ayaa suurtagal ah.
Daaweynta kale ee aan tooska ahayn ee nidaamyada difaaca jirka, tusaale ahaan, isticmaalka monoclonal antibodies, waa mid aad u yar.
Wax soo saarka xayawaanka bukaanka ee ka soo kabsaday bukaanka, oo ah qayb ka mid ah dareeraha dhiigga ee bukaanka, oo leh unugyo difaaca ee loo qoondeeyay fayraska, ayaa laga yaabaa inay kordhiso si loo sii dhaqso u soo bandhigo.
